summary: a smallish sized dwemer dungeon south of windhelm
descriptionHtml:
My First mod uploaded to Nexus ^w^

Zhulhanch is a short length Dwemer Ruins dungeon populated by automatons.  I focused on aesthetics more that anything else while making it, as such; loot is a bit sparse.  The "puzzle" is just a matter of finding the lever or valve that opens the way forward, nothing complex.   Also; you need the attunement sphere to access the lowest level of the dungeon.

Requires the Dawnguard DLC
I don't expect there to be any compatibility issues, since this is just a dungeon, with a very small amount of surface structures.
author: darksaint0523
